<sentence>　<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e101">入賞した</EVENT>作文や絵を<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e102">見ている</EVENT>と、ロケットに<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e103">乗っ</EVENT>て宇宙旅行を<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e104">し</EVENT>たり、宇宙人と<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e105">対話する</EVENT>近未来の夢が<EVENT class="REPORTING" eid="e106">語られ</EVENT>、<EVENT class="NULL" eid="e107">楽しい</EVENT>気分に<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e108">なってくる</EVENT>。</sentence>
