<sentence>　また、<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t9" type="DATE" value="2002" valueFromSurface="XXXX">今年</TIMEX3>は<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t10" type="DATE" value="2002-08-12" valueFromSurface="XXXX-08-12">八月十二日</TIMEX3>から<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t11" type="DATE" value="2002-08-13" valueFromSurface="XXXX-XX-13">十三日</TIMEX3>に<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e121">かけ</EVENT>て全国各地で、<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t12" type="DURATION" value="PT1H" valueFromSurface="PT1H">一時間</TIMEX3>に約百個の星が<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e122">流れる</EVENT>ペルセウス座流星群が<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e123">観測できる</EVENT>可能性が<EVENT class="NULL" eid="e124">高い</EVENT>と<EVENT class="REPORTING" eid="e125">いう</EVENT>。</sentence>
